                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For any non-integer magazine values the magazine size is simply rounded to the nearest whole number. For example, a Angstrum modded with a max rank Tainted Clip will have a calculated magazine size of 3 × (1 + 60%) = 4.8 , which will simply round to 5 ."
